=== 结构 ===

AB与BC考试的结构是一样的。两个考试时长都是3小时15分钟，包括45个[[选择题|选择题]]和6个[[申論題|申論題]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collegeboard.com/student/testing/ap/calculus_ab/exam.html?calcab |title=The Exam |work=Calculus AB |publisher=College Board |date= |accessdate=2008-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219070621/http://www.collegeboard.com/student/testing/ap/calculus_ab/exam.html?calcab |archivedate=2008-12-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>它们的详细分布如下：

